data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1000x700 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Section 6 — Playoff vs Regular Season Performance\n","\n","One of the most important questions for a front office building a championship contender is whether their players perform when it matters most. Regular season statistics can be misleading — some players elevate their game in the playoffs while others struggle against tougher competition and higher defensive intensity. Here we compare each player's scoring, FG%, and plus/minus between the regular season and playoffs, filtering to players with at least 20 regular season games and 5 playoff games to ensure meaningful sample sizes."],"metadata":{"id":"tFAF4Obyqetj"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Merge regular season and playoff stats\n","reg = player_traditional[[\"PLAYER_ID\", \"PLAYER_NAME\", \"SEASON\", \"TEAM_ABBREVIATION\",\n","                           \"GP\", \"PTS\", \"AST\", \"REB\", \"PLUS_MINUS\", \"FG_PCT\"]].copy()\n","play = playoff_traditional[[\"PLAYER_ID\", \"SEASON\", \"GP\", \"PTS\", \"AST\",\n","                             \"REB\", \"PLUS_MINUS\", \"FG_PCT\"]].copy()\n","\n","play = play.rename(columns={\n","    \"GP\": \"PO_GP\", \"PTS\": \"PO_PTS\", \"AST\": \"PO_AST\",\n","    \"REB\": \"PO_REB\", \"PLUS_MINUS\": \"PO_PLUS_MINUS\", \"FG_PCT\": \"PO_FG_PCT\"\n","})\n","\n","# Inner join — only players who appeared in both\n","comparison = reg.merge(play, on=[\"PLAYER_ID\", \"SEASON\"], how=\"inner\")\n","comparison = comparison[(comparison[\"GP\"] >= 20) & (comparison[\"PO_GP\"] >= 5)].copy()\n","\n","# Calculate deltas\n","comparison[\"DELTA_PTS\"]        = comparison[\"PO_PTS\"] - comparison[\"PTS\"]\n","comparison[\"DELTA_PLUS_MINUS\"] = comparison[\"PO_PLUS_MINUS\"] - comparison[\"PLUS_MINUS\"]\n","comparison[\"DELTA_FG_PCT\"]     = comparison[\"PO_FG_PCT\"] - comparison[\"FG_PCT\"]\n","\n","print(\"=\" * 70)\n","print(\"PLAYERS WHO ELEVATE IN THE PLAYOFFS — Best +/- Improvement\")\n","print(\"=\" * 70)\n","print(comparison.nlargest(10, \"DELTA_PLUS_MINUS\")[\n","    [\"PLAYER_NAME\", \"SEASON\", \"TEAM_ABBREVIATION\",\n","     \"PLUS_MINUS\", \"PO_PLUS_MINUS\", \"DELTA_PLUS_MINUS\",\n","     \"PTS\", \"PO_PTS\", \"DELTA_PTS\"]\n","].reset_index(drop=True).to_string())\n","\n","print(\"\\n\")\n","print(\"=\" * 70)\n","print(\"PLAYERS WHO DECLINE IN THE PLAYOFFS — Worst +/- Drop\")\n","print(\"=\" * 70)\n","print(comparison.nsmallest(10, \"DELTA_PLUS_MINUS\")[\n","    [\"PLAYER_NAME\", \"SEASON\", \"TEAM_ABBREVIATION\",\n","     \"PLUS_MINUS\", \"PO_PLUS_MINUS\", \"DELTA_PLUS_MINUS\",\n","     \"PTS\", \"PO_PTS\", \"DELTA_PTS\"]\n","].reset_index(drop=True).to_string())"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"E66Ys8FrqmQM","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1775701935137,"user_tz":420,"elapsed":71,"user":{"displayName":"Faisal Alessa","userId":"15182016480962682188"}},"outputId":"ab465550-0e44-46e8-8965-52d7e8d0438f"},"execution_count":29,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["======================================================================\n","PLAYERS WHO ELEVATE IN THE PLAYOFFS — Best +/- Improvement\n","======================================================================\n","        PLAYER_NAME   SEASON TEAM_ABBREVIATION  PLUS_MINUS  PO_PLUS_MINUS  DELTA_PLUS_MINUS   PTS  PO_PTS  DELTA_PTS\n","0      Jevon Carter  2021-22               MIL        -0.8            5.9               6.7   4.2     2.1       -2.1\n","1      Bobby Portis  2023-24               MIL        -0.1            6.0               6.1  13.8    16.5        2.7\n","2     Javonte Green  2024-25               CLE        -3.1            3.0               6.1   5.1     2.5       -2.6\n","3     Mason Plumlee  2022-23               LAC        -3.4            2.6               6.0  10.8     8.2       -2.6\n","4   De'Andre Hunter  2024-25               CLE         1.4            7.1      