1           -9.2             -13.3  24.2    25.8        1.6\n","9     Monte Morris  2021-22               DEN         3.8           -9.0             -12.8  12.6    14.0        1.4\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Scatter: regular season vs playoff scoring\n","# Players above the diagonal score more in the playoffs than the regular season\n","fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(9, 9))\n","\n","ax.scatter(comparison[\"PTS\"], comparison[\"PO_PTS\"], alpha=0.5, s=50, color=\"#1d428a\")\n","\n","max_pts = max(comparison[\"PTS\"].max(), comparison[\"PO_PTS\"].max())\n","ax.plot([0, max_pts], [0, max_pts], \"r--\", linewidth=1.2, label=\"Same performance\")\n","\n","# Label top elevators\n","for _, row in comparison.nlargest(5, \"DELTA_PTS\").iterrows():\n","    ax.annotate(row[\"PLAYER_NAME\"], (row[\"PTS\"], row[\"PO_PTS\"]),\n","                textcoords=\"offset points\", xytext=(5, 5),\n","                fontsize=8, color=\"#007a33\", fontweight=\"bold\")\n","\n","# Label top decliners\n","for _, row in comparison.nsmallest(5, \"DELTA_PTS\").iterrows():\n","    ax.annotate(row[\"PLAYER_NAME\"], (row[\"PTS\"], row[\"PO_PTS\"]),\n","                textcoords=\"offset points\", xytext=(5, -10),\n","                fontsize=8, color=\"#c8102e\", fontweight=\"bold\")\n","\n","ax.set_xlabel(\"Regular Season PPG\", fontsize=12)\n","ax.set_ylabel(\"Playoff PPG\", fontsize=12)\n","ax.set_title(\"Regular Season vs Playoff Scoring (2021–2025)\\nAbove line = elevated playoff performance\",\n","             fontsize=13, fontweight=\"bold\")\n","ax.legend(fontsize=10)\n","ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n","\n","plt.tight_layout()\n","plt.savefig(\"playoff_vs_regular_scoring.png\", dpi=150)\n","plt.show()"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":906},"id":"vF2JpTcSqqLW","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1775701935739,"user_tz":420,"elapsed":596,"user":{"displayName":"Faisal Alessa","userId":"15182016480962682188"}},"outputId":"70701962-9d96-4b40-90e0-0ca5d80fbd32"},"execution_count":30,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 900x900 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["\n","The players who appear in the upper-left portion of the chart — scoring more in the playoffs than the regular season — are the kinds of players every front office wants on a playoff roster. These players either thrive under pressure, benefit from a more structured offensive system in the postseason, or simply face weaker opponents in early rounds. Players in the lower-right — scoring less in the playoffs — may be overvalued based on regular season production alone."],"metadata":{"id":"oVsu5j1NqekG"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Section 7 — Hustle Stats: Finding Hidden Value\n","\n","Box score statistics and even advanced metrics can miss a significant portion of a player's contribution. Hustle stats — deflections, contested shots, charges drawn, and screen assists — capture the effort-based contributions that don't show up in a traditional stat line but have a measurable impact on winning. Players who rank highly on hustle metrics relative to their scoring output are often undervalued on the open market, making them ideal targets for cost-efficient roster construction."],"metadata":{"id":"Ysz3_5B2q7Y6"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Drop columns from hustle that already exist in traditional stats to avoid conflicts\n","hustle_clean = player_hustle.drop(columns=[\"PLAYER_NAME\", \"TEAM_ABBREVIATION\",\n","                                            \"TEAM_ID\", \"AGE\", \"G\", \"MIN\"]).copy()\n","\n","hustle_merged = hustle_clean.merge(\n","    player_traditional[[\"PLAYER_ID\", \"SEASON\", \"PLAYER_NAME\",\n","                         \"TEAM_ABBREVIATION\", \"GP\", \"MIN\", \"PTS\"]],\n","    on=[\"PLAYER_ID\", \"SEASON\"], how=\"left\"\n",")\n","\n","# Filter to meaningful playing time using traditional stats columns\n","hustle_merged = hustle_merged[(hustle_merged[\"GP\"] >= 20) & (hustle_merged[\"MIN\"] >= 15)]\n","\n","# Build hustle composite score — equal weight across four effort metrics\n","hustle_merged[\"HUSTLE_SCORE\"] = (\n","    normalize(hustle_merged[\"DEFLECTIONS\"]) +\n","    normalize(hustle_merged[\"CONTESTED_SHOTS\"]) +\n","    normalize(hustle_merged[\"CHARGES_DRAWN\"]) +\n","    normalize(hustle_merged[\"SCREEN_ASSISTS\"])\n",") / 4\n","\n","hustle_2324 = hustle_merged[hustle_merged[\"SEASON\"] == \"2023-24\"].copy()\n","\n","# Hidden value = high hustle relative to scoring profile\n","hustle_2324[\"HIDDEN_VALUE\"] = hustle_2324[\"HUSTLE_SCORE\"] - normalize(hustle_2324[\"PTS\"])\n","\n","print(\"=\" * 70)\n","print(\"HIGH HUSTLE / LOWER SCORING PLAYERS — Hidden Value Targets (2023-24)\")\n","print(\"Players who contribute beyond the box score — ideal role player targets\")\n","print(\"=\" * 70)\n","print(hustle_2324.nlargest(15, \"HIDDEN_VALUE\")[\n","    [\"PLAYER_NAME\", \"TEAM_ABBREVIATION\", \"PTS\", \"DEFLECTIONS\",\n","     \"CONTESTED_SHOTS\", \"CHARGES_DRAWN\", \"SCREEN_ASSISTS\", \"HUSTLE_SCORE\"]\n","].reset_index(drop=True).to_string())"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"JZntsyHiqeV1","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1775701935764,"user_tz":420,"elapsed":20,"user":{"displayName":"Faisal Alessa","userId":"15182016480962682188"}},"outputId":"8c354076-8f37-47d6-9f60-673b935999ad"},"execution_count":31,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["======================================================================\n","HIGH HUSTLE / LOWER SCORING PLAYERS — Hidden Value Targets (2023-24)\n","Players who contribute beyond the box score — ideal role player targets\n","======================================================================\n","           PLAYER_NAME TEAM_ABBREVIATION   PTS  DEFLECTIONS  CONTESTED_SHOTS  CHARGES_DRAWN  SCREEN_ASSISTS  HUSTLE_SCORE\n","0       Draymond Green               GSW   8.6    